How I got the look‼️

✨ Cleanse hair with intense moisturizing cream shampoo 
✨Detangle with Intensive Moisturizing Mask in small sections from ends to roots. The slip is amazing! 
✨ Part hair in four sections and apply long- lasting Intensive Moisturizer from ends to roots. 
✨Apply Cream- In Jelly Definition Activator over Moisturizer and rake cream in 1/2 inch section from root to ends for more defined curls. Scrunch curls up for more volume before drying.

To protect my clients curls I used @lorealpro Metal Detox Collection! Hair has 100% reliable color and 87% less breakage.  #afterdetox #lorealpropartner #lorealpro #metaldetox
